  "texts": [
    "Our IR component uses data from PubMed database 3 containing citations and biomedical literature from several literature resources.",
    "The IR system integrates both sparse vectors (lexical index) and dense vectors (semantic index), enabling lexical and semantic search, and a hybrid combination of the two.",
    "For the lexical retrieval, based on a ranking function Best Matching 25 (BM25), we use the OpenSearch 4 to create an index for PubMed articles, by concatenation of title and abstract as an indexed field.",
    "Also, we add authors' names, pub- lication dates, and journal names as metadata for filtering.",
    "For semantic retrieval, based on dense vectors, we use the Qdrant foot_2 vector database."
  ],
